FORGE вҖ” Build Plan

> Unified MCP orchestrator for Blender, Unreal Engine 5, and Adobe Premiere Pro.  
> Model, render, and edit from a single prompt.

---

What FORGE Is

FORGE is a multi-app MCP orchestration layer that connects three professional creative tools вҖ” Blender, Unreal Engine 5, and Adobe Premiere Pro вҖ” to Claude via the Model Context Protocol. Instead of switching between applications and manually transferring render outputs, you describe what you want in a single natural language prompt and FORGE handles the sequencing, execution, and file handoff across the entire pipeline.

A single prompt like:

> "Render the campfire scene from Blender at 1080p, wait for the output, then import it into the current Premiere sequence on track V2 and cut it at the 4-second mark."

...executes across all three applications without you touching any of them.

