Configuration вҖ” forge.yaml

```yaml
# FORGE pipeline configuration
# Copy forge.example.yaml to forge.yaml and edit for your project

pipeline:
  render_output: D:/forge/renders/
  fps: 24
  default_format: EXR        # EXR | PNG | MP4

blender:
  port: 9876
  default_scene: ""          # optional: path to .blend file

unreal:
  port: 55557
  project_path: ""           # optional: path to .uproject

premiere:
  temp_dir: /tmp/premiere-mcp-bridge
  default_sequence: ""       # optional: sequence name to target

watcher:
  poll_interval_ms: 500      # how often to check for new render files
  stabilize_delay_ms: 1000   # wait after file appears before signalling done
```

